{"tid":2194628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《港版国安法》中国書評網上架　評一星用戶帳號永久被封","createTime":"2020-09-08T15:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T15:24:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f73e88a2ee1b4e3e84f2c1bdc89940adfb603da6","tid":2194628,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"中國書評網豆瓣在上月上架「港版國安法」刊物《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法全國人民代表大會關於建立健全香港特別行政區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制的決定》，惟評分持續偏低。近日有中國網民指，現時只要在豆瓣上給予該書低分，就會遭到禁言，而平台更在其後取消該書目的評分及評論功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/thumbnail-e1599567176433.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fthumbnail-e1599567176433.jpeg&h=512f1c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國網民在 Twitter 上指，在豆瓣上給予「港版國安法」刊物一星評分的用戶都遭禁言一個月，而近日情況更是加劇，連帳號也被永久停用。網民表示該平台的做法相當下流，更指完全不能接受相關做法。<br />\n<br />\n而目前，該書目的評分及評論功能似乎己被停用，直接變成沒有任何評分，而評論亦已被悉數刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/%E8%B1%86%E7%93%A3%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6-1024x760-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F%25E8%25B1%2586%25E7%2593%25A3%25E8%25AF%25BB%25E4%25B9%25A6-1024x760-1.jpg&h=9f925207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/09/08/douban-2/hottopic/spotlight/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F08%2Fdouban-2%2Fhottopic%2Fspotlight%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNeojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=cd23576d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/09/08/douban-2/hottopic/spotlight/</a>"},{"pid":"dfbc3bbbe3bd90df224f78bad8276ec98775d352","tid":2194628,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/siusiu902/status/1302965726672642048?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsiusiu902%2Fstatus%2F1302965726672642048%3Fs%3D20&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNeojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=93ab5b11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsiusiu902%2Fstatus%2F1302965726672642048%3Fs%3D20&h=59ca3559\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/siusiu902/status/1302965726672642048?s=20</a>"}]}